 of construction superintendent to assist \n  Dan<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></B></LI></UL>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><B \nstyle=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" \nsize=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></B></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><B \nstyle=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><FONT size=3><FONT \nface=\"Times New Roman\">Thank you,<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></B></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><B \nstyle=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" \nsize=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></B></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><B \nstyle=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><FONT size=3><FONT \nface=\"Times New Roman\">Charles<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></B></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><B \nstyle=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" \nsize=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></B></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><B \nstyle=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" \nsize=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><FONT \nsize=3><FONT \nface=\"Times New Roman\">__________________________________<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></B></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><B \nstyle=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><FONT size=3><FONT \nface=\"Times New Roman\">APPROVED<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></B></P></DIV></FONT><BR><BR><BR><DIV><FONT style=\"color: black; font: normal 10pt ARIAL, SAN-SERIF;\"><HR style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 10px\">It's Tax Time! <A title=\"http://money.aol.com/tax?NCID=aolprf00030000000001\" href=\"http://money.aol.com/tax?NCID=aolprf00030000000001\" target=\"_blank\">Get tips, forms and advice on AOL Money & Finance.</A></FONT></DIV></BODY></HTML>\n","is_from_epstein":false,"attachments":1,"avatar_color":"#4285f4","stars":1,"is_redacted":false}]